com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto

Interface IProcessAreaScope

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IReadScope

    public interface IProcessAreaScope
extends IReadScope
    An item with this scope is owned by a process area. The read access of the process area controls who can view the item.
    Since:
    0.8.1.
